{"type":"message","id":"f77b72ac","parentId":"83ed4297","timestamp":"2026-06-09T00:59:09.054Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me analyze what we actually have:\n\n**TikTok tools (VN/TH available):**\n- `tiktok_category_name_search` - search categories by name\n- `tiktok_category_report` - get category report with Top products (nodeId based)\n- `tiktok_product_detail` - single product detail\n- `tiktok_product_trend` - single product trend (sales, price, rating, video count)\n- `tiktok_similar_product` - search similar products by name (20 per page)\n- `tiktok_product_video` -带货视频列表\n- `tiktok_product_video_author` - 带货达人\n\n\n- `tiktok_author` - search creators\n\n**Shopee tools (VN/TH available):**\n- `shopee_category_search_from_name` - search categories\n- `shopee_category_request` - category report with top products\n- `shopee_category_trend` - category trend data (MonthlySalesVolume, etc.)\n- `shopee_product_search` - search products with filters (nodeId, price, monthly sales, etc.)\n- `shopee_product_search_from_name` - search by name\n- `shopee_product_request` - single product detail\n- `shopee_product_trend` - product trend history\n- `shopee_shop_request` - shop detail\n- `shopee_keyword_search` - search keywords\n- `shopee_keyword_relation_results` - keyword relations\n- `shopee_favorite_keyword` - keyword favorites management\n\n**1688:**\n- `ali1688_similar_product` - search 1688 by product name\n\n**Amazon:**\n- `potential_product` - search Amazon for potential products\n- `category_report` - Amazon category report\n- `product_trend` - Amazon product trend\n- `product_search` - Amazon product search\n\nSo the real workflow is: use Shopee's category data to spot trending products with strong sales and reviews, then cross-reference those products across TikTok and Amazon to validate demand, find similar items, and check for seasonality or trends.\n\nThe critical realization is that I'm doing this backwards—I should be leveraging Shopee's superior search and filtering capabilities to surface high-potential products first, then validating them on TikTok for momentum, rather than starting blind on TikTok. Let me restructure this around that insight and build out the SOP, starting with a quick validation of the actual data returned.\n","thinkingSignature":"058dc785eeb0f47e101564128d9ab0019eff9d51ae02cbfa8e9cd2a30b7c08a7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n现在我看清全貌了。让我先实测几个关键接口，搞清楚数据实际长什么样：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bad4869c1ac048128c6c0bb1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \"key not in tmp\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a752718c9b7e46058ff35ee9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 先测Shopee越南发饰类目趋势 - 最有价值的起点数据\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp shopee_category_trend '{\"nodeId\": \"11035541\", \"trendIndex\": \"MonthlySalesVolume\", \"site\": \"VN\"}' 2>/dev/null | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8271,"output":658,"cacheRead":63012,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780966726488,"responseId":"06769847ceca881c8b5fd3830c26b616"}}
