{"type":"message","id":"5767010e","parentId":"7a238eae","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:17:26.178Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is reminding me to reply in Chinese, not English. I should write the SOP in Chinese. Let me continue working on the SOP and respond in Chinese.\n\nI've been testing the Sorftime API and now understand:\n- Shopee product search works well with filters\n- 1688 similar product search works\n- The key insight: use Shopee as the primary source for product discovery (it's the most powerful filterable search), then verify with TikTok trend, then check 1688 for sourcing\n\nLet me now write the new SOP in Chinese. The core idea:\n1. **Shopee product_search** → 越南/泰国站点，按销量+价格+评分筛选发饰类目\n\n\n2. **Shopee product_trend** → 看历史趋势，找增长品\n3. **ali1688_similar_product** → 找货源和采购价\n4. **毛利率计算** → 售价-1688价×汇率-物流-佣金\n\nFor the SOP, I need to be realistic about what the data actually shows - there's no 24-hour sales data available, only weekly metrics, and VN TikTok videos are sparse. The SOP should focus on Shopee as the primary source since it has the most comprehensive filtering and trend data.\n","thinkingSignature":"8235ceaa4425900dedfafd79120153cdb9fc4480bb6ff12924da407e720eb241"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，继续搞。继续测数据然后写 SOP：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3d7375ec2d844559b00ad32d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 越南发夹类目，按增长排序搜索（验证API数据）\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://mcp.sorftime.com/\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ***…qt09\" \\\n  -H \"accept: application/json, text/event-stream\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"VN\",\"nodeId\":\"11035861\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":50,\"priceRangeMin\":20000,\"page\":1}},\"id\":8}' 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nraw = sys.stdin.read()\n# 提取JSON\nstart = raw.find('{\\\"result\\\"')\ndata = json.loads(start)\ncontent = data['result']['content'][0]['text']\nproducts = json.loads(content)['Products'][:8]\nfor p in products:\n    print(f\\\"{p['Title'][:35]} | 月销:{p['SalesCount']} | 7天:{p['SalesCountOf7D']} | 增长:{p['MonthlySalesGrowth']}% | 价:{p['Price']} | 星级:{p['Ratings']}\\\")\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":138777,"output":562,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139339,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780989400549,"responseId":"0676f0d9cdfbf8d6ee761b72be5eddef"}}
