{"type":"message","id":"0bf13b8d","parentId":"1ceab755","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:18:06.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Authentication required! The earlier successful calls must have been cached or used a different auth. Wait - earlier the same curl command worked (get_time, ali1688_similar_product, shopee_category_search_from_name, shopee_product_search for TH all worked). But now they're failing with \"Authentication required\"?\n\nLet me check the key again. Maybe the Bearer token with \"…\" in the middle is being parsed differently by curl vs the actual key file. Earlier calls with `rhblyi…qt09` (using the … character) worked. Let me check if the key in /tmp/sorftime_key.txt is the full correct key.\n","thinkingSignature":"29564790848f65c6e649ab855c92aeb69b98a0daa0dbb7bcf3642890696f9a92"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2e4c5b20a9e746d5a9e9dc81","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt && echo \"---\" && wc -c /tmp/sorftime_key.txt"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7308,"output":178,"cacheRead":132665,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140151,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780989476427,"responseId":"0676f12419a605530b4c547b5490e04e"}}
