\\\\\",\\\\\\\"method\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"tools/call\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"params\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"tiktok_similar_product\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"arguments\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"searchName\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"产品关键词\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"site\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"VN\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"page\\\\\\\":1}},\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":2}'\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n**注意：越南TikTok带货视频数据基本为空，不要用视频数量作为筛选条件。**\\\\n\\\\n## 第三步：1688 利润终选\\\\n用 `ali1688_similar_product` 查货源：\\\\n```bash\\\\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\\\\\\\\\\n  -H \\\\\\\"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\\\\\\\" \\\\\\\\\\\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\\\\\\\\\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\\\\\\\\\\n  -d '{\\\\\\\"jsonrpc\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2.0\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"method\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"tools/call\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"params\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ali1688_similar_product\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"arguments\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"searchName\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"产品标题前50字符\\\\\\\"}},\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":3}'\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n**毛利率公式（越南）：**\\\\n- 毛利率 = 售价×55% - 1688价×汇率/售价\\\\n- 越南固定成本 ≈ 45%（平台30%+物流10%+仓储5%）\\\\n- 汇率：1 CNY ≈ 3500 VND\\\\n\\\\n**通过条件：**\\\\n- 1688采购价 ≤ ¥5\\\\n- 毛利率 ≥ 40%\\\\n\\\\n## 第四步：写入飞书多维表格\\\\n- app_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\\\\n- table_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\\\\n- 20个字段全填，不留空\\\\n\\\\n## 第五步：发送飞书选品报告\\\\n- 包含：通过数量、等级分布（S/A/B/C）、核心爆款信息\\\\n- 站点标注：越南\\\"}}, \\\"delivery\\\": {\\\"mode\\\": \\\"announce\\\", \\\"channel\\\": \\\"feishu\\\", \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"tts\\\"}}\"\n}"}],"details":{},"isError":true,"timestamp":1780989625910}}
{"type":"message","id":"d235f9d1","parentId":"e2359e55","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:20:35.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The patch needs to be a proper object, not a JSON string. Let me try using the edit tool approach differently - or use a proper patch format. Actually, looking at the cron schema more carefully, the `patch` should be an object (not a string), and the fields should be at the top level of the patch object, not nested inside. Let me try the correct format.\n\nActually the issue is the JSON string I passed was escaped. Let me use the exec tool to directly call the cron API in a different way.\n\nActually, looking at the cron schema again, the patch format should be the same as the job object but only partial. Let me just delete and recreate the job instead.","thinkingSignature":"75c17f35d17e87abc082861ca8d32fc88d9719a9ec5b338debd9dbdd6f6c5f30"},{"type":"text","text":"格式问题，我删掉重建：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_je6mcr2w2nnn_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"remove","jobId":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94103,"output":208,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148485,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780989625949,"responseId":"0676f1bae19f9c88f82d6791260c2628"}}
