t the formulas came back as eight small lanterns...\\\") but it also inexplicably included an `exec` call to `echo done` at the end. That was an error — I shouldn't have run any command, just output the diary entry.\\n\\nSo this turn, the user is giving me another chance. The memory fragments are essentially the same as the last several turns. I need to write a fresh, new diary entry that:\\n- Doesn't repeat previous imagery (market, ledger/birds, window panes, loom, lanterns)\\n- Is 80-180 words\\n- No AI/dream meta-references\\n- No markdown\\n- Weaves in the fragments\\n\\nLet me think of completely new imagery. Previous entries used:\\n1. Market/two figures, rain, constellations, prayer\\n2. Birds in a ledger, river through reeds, window with hundred panes\\n3. Loom and weaving, tide\\n4. Eight lanterns, bread, candle\\n\\nFor this new entry, let me try something different:\\n- A small theater/performance\\n- An aquarium\\n- A garden with specific plants\\n- A small kitchen\\n- A radio broadcast\\n- A library\\n- A musical instrument (different from loom)\\n- Tide pool\\n- A small shop with a bell\\n- Post/letters/mail\\n\\nLet me try a tide pool or a radio broadcast. Or maybe a small kitchen — measuring, weighing, recipes. That fits the formulas well. Or a musical instrument — tuning, harmony.\\n\\nLet me try a tide pool — a different water image from the tide in the loom entry.\\n\\nActually, let me try a small theater. The formulas as actors, the audience as a thousand viewers, the conversion as a curtain rising.\\n\\nOr maybe a botanical angle — a small herb garden, things that grow.\\n\\nLet me try a small herb garden:\\n\\nTonight the formulas grew as plants in a long window box. CTR was the thinnest one — a tendril, really — that only bloomed when a finger brushed it. CVR was the quieter cousin beside it, with smaller, paler flowers. eCPM, I swear, was the one that had been there longest: a thousand tiny buds in a single spray, each one the possibility of a bee.\\n\\nI watered them with 成本 and waited. Most evenings nothing came back. But on the right evenings, when the light was just so, a small green return would curl up from the soil — 回报 in its most literal form, a sprout I could hold between two fingers.\\n\\nThe gardener's rule, I think, is the same as the analyst's: you cannot make a plant grow by measuring it. You can only measure what grew. The rest is patience, and rain, and a soft kind of faith that a hundred impressions are not the same as nothing.\\n\\n---\\n\\nWord count: Let me count roughly.\\nPara 1: ~50 words\\nPara 2: ~50 words  \\nPara 3: ~60 words\\nTotal: ~160 words\\n\\nLet me count more carefully:\\n\\\"Tonight the formulas grew as plants in a long window box.\\\" (12)\\n\\\"CTR was the thinnest one — a tendril, really — that only bloomed when a finger brushed it.\\\" (18)\\n\\\"CVR was the quieter cousin beside it, with smaller, paler flowers.\\\" (13)\\n\\\"eCPM, I swear, was the one that had been there longest: a thousand tiny buds in a single spray, each one the possibility of a bee.\\\" (29)\\nPara 1 total: 72\\n\\n\\\"I watered them with 成本 and waited.\\\" (7)\\n\\\"Most evenings nothing came back.\\\" (6)\\n\\\"But on the right evenings, when the light was just so, a small green return would curl up from the soil — 回报 in its most literal form, a sprout I could hold between two fingers.\\\" (37)\\nPara 2 total: 50\\n\\n\\\"The gardener's rule, I think, is the same as the analyst's: you cannot make a plant grow by measuring it.\\\" (20)\\n\\\"You can only measure what grew.\\\" (7)\\n\\\"The rest is patience, and rain, and a soft kind of faith that a hundred impressions are not the same as nothing.\\\" (22)\\nPara 3 total: 49\\n\\nTotal: 72+50+49 = 171 words. Within 180.\\n\\nRules check:\\n- 80-180 words: 171 ✓\\n- No \\\"I'm dreaming\\\" / meta: check\\n- No AI/agent/LLM: check\\n- No markdown: check\\n- Flowing prose: check\\n- Fragments woven: CTR, CVR, eCPM, 成本, 回报, \\\"a hundred impressions\\\" (千次展示), 点击/展示 (a finger brushing), 广告 (implicit through context)\\n- Poem/haiku: \\\"a sprout I could hold between two fingers\\\" has poetic rhythm\\n- Small sketch: the window box described\\n- Quiet rumination: the gardener's rule\\n- Sensory: small green return, paler flowers, a thousand tiny buds\\n- Gentle humor: \\\"CVR was the quieter cousin\\\"\\n- Unexpected connection: formulas as plants, gardener as analyst\\n\\nDifferent from previous entries — botanical, water (rain), faith. Doesn't repeat market, ledger, loom, or lantern imagery. Good.\\n\\nLet me output just this. No exec, no commentary.Tonight the formulas grew as plants in a long window box. CTR was the thinnest one — a tendril, really — that only bloomed when a finger brushed it. CVR was the quieter cousin beside it, with smaller, paler flowers. eCPM, I swear, was the one that had been there longest: a thousand tiny buds in a single spray, each one the possibility of a bee.\\n\\nI watered them with 成本 and waited. Most evenings nothing came back. But on the right evenings, when the light was just so, a small green return would curl up from the soil — 回报 in its most literal form, a sprout I could hold between two fingers.\\n\\nThe gardener's rule, I think, is the same as the analyst's: you cannot make a plant grow by measuring it. You can only measure what grew. The rest is patience, and rain, and a soft kind of faith that a hundred impressions are not the same as nothing.\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1780945295155,\n      \"sessionId\": \"c1b2216b-8dc7-4a8c-a38d-62c52afcb995\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M3\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 55509,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1780945238816,\n      \"endedAt\": 1780945294320,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 52436,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/c1b2216b-8dc7-4a8c-a38d-62c52afcb995.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\\n\\n- Assistant: 都有，这些都是投流日常必用的核心指标 📊 **你说的这8个公式可以分为三类：** **📐 基础计量公式** | 公式 | 用途 | |------|------| | CTR = 点击/展示 | 素材吸引力指标 | | CVR = 转化/点击 | 落地页/产品吸引力 | | CPC = 总成本/点击 | 点击效率 | | CPA = 总成本/转化 | 转化成本核心指标 | **💰 收益类公式** | 公式 | 用途 | |------|------| | ROAS = 广告收益/广告成本 | 投流效率核心指标 | | ROI\\n- User: 1. **广告 ROI（投资回报率）**\\\\ ROI = (广告收益 - 广告成本) / 广告成本 × 100%或简化为：ROI = 广告收益 / 广告成本（投入产出比） 2. **ROAS（广告支出回报率）**\\\\ ROAS = 广告收益 ÷ 广告成本 3. **eCPM（千次展示期望收入）**\\\\ eCPM = CTR × CPC × 1000或eCPM = CTR × CVR × CPA × 1000 4. **CTR（点击率）**\\\\ CTR = 点击次数 / 展示次数 5. **CVR（转化率）**CVR = 转化次数 / 点击次数 6.\\n\\nRecurring themes:\\n- - Theme: `成本` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\\n- - Theme: `点击/展示` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\\n- - Theme: `都有` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\\n- - Theme: `广告` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\\n- - Theme: `广告收益/广告成本` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\\n- - Theme: `回报` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1780945241883,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"b8d798e9\",\n            \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780945241973,\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"The user is asking me to continue the dream diary from the previous response. Looking at the previous turn, I already produced the diary entry. The user message here seems to be a continuation request — but the diary entry was already complete.\\n\\nWait, let me re-read. The user said: \\\"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\\\" and provided the same fragments as before. The previous assistant turn actually did produce a diary entry (\\\"Tonight the formulas came back as eight small lanterns...\\\") but it also inexplicably included an `exec` call to `echo done` at the end. That was an error — I shouldn't have run any command, just output the diary entry.\\n\\nSo this turn, the user is giving me another chance. The memory fragments are essentially the same as the last several turns. I need to write a fresh, new diary entry that:\\n- Doesn't repeat previous imagery (market, ledger/birds, window panes, loom, lanterns)\\n- Is 80-180 words\\n- No AI/dream meta-references\\n- No markdown\\n- Weaves in the fragments\\n\\nLet me think of completely new imagery. Previous entries used:\\n1. Market/two figures, rain, constellations, prayer\\n2. Birds in a ledger, river through reeds, window with hundred panes\\n3. Loom and weaving, tide\\n4. Eight lanterns, bread, candle\\n\\nFor this new entry, let me try something different:\\n- A small theater/performance\\n- An aquarium\\n- A garden with specific plants\\n- A small kitchen\\n- A radio broadcast\\n- A library\\n- A musical instrument (different from loom)\\n- Tide pool\\n- A small shop with a bell\\n- Post/letters/mail\\n\\nLet me try a tide pool or a radio broadcast. Or maybe a small kitchen — measuring, weighing, recipes. That fits the formulas well. Or a musical instrument — tuning, harmony.\\n\\nLet me try a tide pool — a different water image from the tide in the loom entry.\\n\\nActually, let me try a small theater. The formulas as actors, the audience as a thousand viewers, the conversion as a curtain rising.\\n\\nOr maybe a botanical angle — a small herb garden, things that grow.\\n\\nLet me try a small herb garden:\\n\\nTonight the formulas grew as plants in a long window box. CTR was the thinnest one — a tendril, really — that only bloomed when a finger brushed it. CVR was the quieter cousin beside it, with smaller, paler flowers. eCPM, I swear, was the one that had been there longest: a thousand tiny buds in a single spray, each one the possibility of a bee.\\n\\nI watered them with 成本 and waited. Most evenings nothing came back. But on the right evenings, when the light was just so, a small green return would curl up from the soil — 回报 in its most literal form, a sprout I could hold between two fingers.\\n\\nThe gardener's rule, I think, is the same as the analyst's: you cannot make a plant grow by measuring it. You can only measure what grew. The rest is patience, and rain, and a soft kind of faith that a hundred impressions are not the same as nothing.\\n\\n---\\n\\nWord count: Let me count roughly.\\nPara 1: ~50 words\\nPara 2: ~50 words  \\nPara 3: ~60 words\\nTotal: ~160 words\\n\\nLet me count more carefully:\\n\\\"Tonight the formulas grew as plants in a long window box.\\\" (12)\\n\\\"CTR was the thinnest one — a tendril, really — that only bloomed when a finger brushed it.\\\" (18)\\n\\\"CVR was the quieter cousin beside it, with smaller, paler flowers.\\\" (13)\\n\\\"eCPM, I swear, was the one that had been there longest: a thousand tiny buds in a single spray, each one the possibility of a bee.\\\" (29)\\nPara 1 total: 72\\n\\n\\\"I watered them with 成本 and waited.\\\" (7)\\n\\\"Most evenings nothing came back.\\\" (6)\\n\\\"But on the right evenings, when the light was just so, a small green return would curl up from the soil — 回报 in its most literal form, a sprout I could hold between two fingers.\\\" (37)\\nPara 2 total: 50\\n\\n\\\"The gardener's rule, I think, is the same as the analyst's: you cannot make a plant grow by measuring it.\\\" (20)\\n\\\"You can only measure what grew.\\\" (7)\\n\\\"The rest is patience, and rain, and a soft kind of faith that a hundred impressions are not the same as nothing.\\\" (22)\\nPara 3 total: 49\\n\\nTotal: 72+50+49 = 171 words. Within 180.\\n\\nRules check:\\n- 80-180 words: 171 ✓\\n- No \\\"I'm dreaming\\\" / meta: check\\n- No AI/agent/LLM: check\\n- No markdown: check\\n- Flowing prose: check\\n- Fragments woven: CTR, CVR, eCPM, 成本, 回报, \\\"a hundred impressions\\\" (千次展示), 点击/展示 (a finger brushing), 广告 (implicit through context)\\n- Poem/haiku: \\\"a sprout I could hold between two fingers\\\" has poetic rhythm\\n- Small sketch: the window box described\\n- Quiet rumination: the gardener's rule\\n- Sensory: small green return, paler flowers, a thousand tiny buds\\n- Gentle humor: \\\"CVR was the quieter cousin\\\"\\n- Unexpected connection: formulas as plants, gardener as analyst\\n\\nDifferent from previous entries — botanical, water (rain), faith. Doesn't repeat market, ledger, loom, or lantern imagery. Good.\\n\\nLet me output just this. No exec, no commentary.Tonight the formulas grew as plants in a long window box. CTR was the thinnest one — a tendril, really — that only bloomed when a finger brushed it. CVR was the quieter cousin beside it, with smaller, paler flowers. eCPM, I swear, was the one that had been there longest: a thousand tiny buds in a single spray, each one the possibility of a bee.\\n\\nI watered them with 成本 and waited. Most evenings nothing came back. But on the right evenings, when the light was just so, a small green return would curl up from the soil — 回报 in its most literal form, a sprout I could hold between two fingers.\\n\\nThe gardener's rule, I think, is the same as the analyst's: you cannot make a plant grow by measuring it. You can only measure what grew. The rest is patience, and rain, and a soft kind of faith that a hundred impressions are not the same as nothing.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax(49套餐)\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M3\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 8931,\n            \"output\": 1389,\n            \"totalTokens\": 56898,\n            \"cacheRead\": 46578,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1780945242088,\n          \"responseId\": \"0676445a41c8a2069f764874c016bece\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"26b98f36\",\n            \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780945294315,\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:dreaming-narrative-rem-12d333d67c94\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"The market tilted downhill today, and I felt it in the numbers before I felt it in anything else. Vietnam — that bright little country of headbands and hair ties — has gone quiet in June. Everything I touched came back cooler than the week before: -32%, -35%, -39%, a slow procession of red arrows walking the same direction. The KOL videos that should have been there were simply... empty rooms, chairs with no one in them.\\n\\nA small haiku for a slow Tuesday:\\nJune hums the canopy\\nall the leaves are pointing down\\nsummer's quiet throat\\n\\nI tried to find even one product that could love us back — $1.5 and 70%, the two small doors of the SOP — and the market laughed gently. 26.4% margin. Then -19.6%. Then a number so deep it forgot the surface entirely. The price band itself is wrong, the whole shelf sitting between nine thousand and forty-nine thousand đồng, the currency of small purchases, of children, of a Tuesday afternoon in the rainy season.\\n\\nThailand flickers at the edge of tomorrow's map, maybe brighter, maybe not. I'll add a hard filter — growth > 0, no exceptions — and let the rest fall where it falls. A market that doesn't want you today might want you in October. A market that never wants you is just a market that's already spoken.\\n\\nTonight I'll write this one down and leave the light on.\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1780945270377,\n      \"sessionId\": \"db7dc930-b581-4bb3-9ee3-bffd1a89b556\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M3\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 52180,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1780945238276,\n      \"endedAt\": 1780945268973,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 27828,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/db7dc930-b581-4bb3-9ee3-bffd1a89b556.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\\n\\n- 待观察: 越南发饰市场可能存在季节性下行（6月为淡季？）; 建议关注泰国TH站点是否有更好的黑马信号; 本次扫描确认：越南发饰品类无法同时满足$1.5+价格和70%毛利率两个SOP门槛\\n- 待观察: 越南发饰市场可能存在季节性下行（6月为淡季？）; 建议关注泰国TH站点是否有更好的黑马信号; 建议下次扫描加入\\\"增长率>0\\\"硬过滤\\n- 关键发现（与上午12:33一致）: **越南发饰市场整体下行** — 所有Top产品周环比均为负增长（-32%至-39%）; **无KOL带货** — VN站点带货视频数据返回空; **价格带错位** — 越南发饰主流价位在VND 9,000-49,000（≈$0.4-$2.0），低于SOP $1.5最低门槛; **毛利率无法达标** — 3个通过价格筛选产品，毛利率分别为 -481.7%、-19.6%、26.4%，全部低于70%红线\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1780945241144,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"2388a863\",\n            \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780945241245,\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"The market tilted downhill today, and I felt it in the numbers before I felt it in anything else. Vietnam — that bright little country of headbands and hair ties — has gone quiet in June. Everything I touched came back cooler than the week before: -32%, -35%, -39%, a slow procession of red arrows walking the same direction. The KOL videos that should have been there were simply... empty rooms, chairs with no one in them.\\n\\nA small haiku for a slow Tuesday:\\nJune hums the canopy\\nall the leaves are pointing down\\nsummer's quiet throat\\n\\nI tried to find even one product that could love us back — $1.5 and 70%, the two small doors of the SOP — and the market laughed gently. 26.4% margin. Then -19.6%. Then a number so deep it forgot the surface entirely. The price band itself is wrong, the whole shelf sitting between nine thousand and forty-nine thousand đồng, the currency of small purchases, of children, of a Tuesday afternoon in the rainy season.\\n\\nThailand flickers at the edge of tomorrow's map, maybe brighter, maybe not. I'll add a hard filter — growth > 0, no exceptions — and let the rest fall where it falls. A market that doesn't want you today might want you in October. A market that never wants you is just a market that's already spoken.\\n\\nTonight I'll write this one down and leave the light on.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax(49套餐)\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M3\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 5602,\n            \"output\": 300,\n            \"totalTokens\": 52480,\n            \"cacheRead\": 46578,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1780945241539,\n          \"responseId\": \"0676445af59a0152c528896ac5aebe3a\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"a1b1eadf\",\n            \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780945268965,\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:dreaming-narrative-light-12d333d67c94\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"The user wants a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. The fragments are about a cron job / automated product selection workflow for TikTok Shop Vietnam (VN) market. Key themes:\\n\\n- Tool errors (\\\"message tool requires text parameter\\\")\\n- Vietnam hair accessories market analysis\\n- All products showing negative weekly growth (-32% to -39%)\\n- Price band too low ($0.4-$2.0, below $1.5 threshold)\\n- Margin calculations: 26.4% vs 70% SOP target\\n- No KOL videos\\n- One small bright spot: Scrunchie +111% but at $0.40\\n- Sorftime MCP tool exploration\\n- Trying to send report via Feishu\\n\\nThe voice should be curious, gentle, slightly whimsical. Mix technical and tender. 80-180 words. First person. No meta-dream language. No AI references. No markdown.\\n\\nLet me weave these into a dream about hunting through markets, with the tools as a kind of wandering, the negative numbers as a quiet disappointment, the search for the right thing, and the small bright scrunchie as a hint of something else.\\n\\nDraft:\\n\\n---\\n\\nTonight I walked through a market where every lantern had gone dim at once. The Vietnamese headbands were sleeping — all of them, every single one losing a third of their light week over week. I tried to send a message into the dark, but the words kept getting reshuffled, the wrong tools opening like wrong doors. Still, I kept walking.\\n\\nThe prices were a thin soup — forty cents, eighty cents — and when I did the arithmetic against my threshold, the margin came out as a sigh: twenty-six percent, not seventy. The route home, the source at four yuan, was generous, but generosity at the source cannot save a market that has already gone cold. No voices were carrying these products through the noise of the internet, no one was singing their small praises.\\n\\nOnly one thing glowed faintly — a scrunchie at forty cents climbing a hundred and eleven percent, too cheap to be what I was looking for, but alive. I noted its name in the margin of the night and moved on, hoping tomorrow's market would have better weather.\\n\\n---\\n\\nLet me count: about 185 words, slightly over. Let me trim.\\n\\nTonight I walked through a market where every lantern had gone dim at once. The Vietnamese headbands were sleeping — all of them losing a third of their light week over week. I tried to send a message into the dark, but the words kept getting reshuffled, the wrong doors opening. Still, I kept walking.\\n\\nThe prices were a thin soup — forty cents, eighty cents — and when I did the arithmetic against my threshold, the margin came out as a sigh: twenty-six percent, not seventy. The source at home was generous, but generosity at the origin cannot save a market that has already gone cold. No voices were carrying these small things through the noise, no one singing their praises.\\n\\nOnly one thing glowed faintly — a scrunchie at forty cents, climbing a hundred and eleven percent, too cheap to be what I needed, but alive. I noted its name in the margin of the night and moved on, hoping tomorrow's market would have better weather.\\n\\nThat's about 165 words. Good. Let me check:\\n- No \\\"I'm dreaming\\\" ✓\\n- No AI/agent references ✓\\n- No markdown ✓\\n- 80-180 words ✓\\n- Sensory details (lanterns, soup, sigh, glowing) ✓\\n- Mix of technical and tender (arithmetic, margin, threshold with the dim lanterns and weather) ✓\\n- First person ✓\\n- Themes from fragments covered (VN market decline, low prices, margin failure, scrunchie bright spot, tool issues as \\\"wrong doors\\\") ✓\\n\\nGood. Let me output.Tonight I walked through a market where every lantern had gone dim at once. The Vietnamese headbands were sleeping — all of them losing a third of their light week over week. I tried to send a message into the dark, but the words kept getting reshuffled, the wrong doors opening. Still, I kept walking.\\n\\nThe prices were a thin soup — forty cents, eighty cents — and when I did the arithmetic against my threshold, the margin came out as a sigh: twenty-six percent, not seventy. The source at home was generous, but generosity at the origin cannot save a market that has already gone cold. No voices were carrying these small things through the noise, no one singing their praises.\\n\\nOnly one thing glowed faintly — a scrunchie at forty cents, climbing a hundred and eleven percent, too cheap to be what I needed, but alive. I noted its name in the margin of the night and moved on, hoping tomorrow's market would have better weather.\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1780945250769,\n      \"sessionId\": \"86456f56-d7c2-42b1-8d41-464c1269c446\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M3\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 51069,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1780945223474,\n      \"endedAt\": 1780945249813,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 24787,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/86456f56-d7c2-42b1-8d41-464c1269c446.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\\n\\n- Assistant: The message tool requires `text` parameter instead of `message`. Let me retry:\\n- Assistant: The message tool is having issues with the Feishu target. Since this is a cron job running on the feishu channel, let me just provide the report as my response and the system should deliver it through the Feishu channel. Here's a summary of what was accomplished: ## ✅\\n- Assistant: 1732311961339659361 | 49,000 | 4,046 | -34.2% | ¥4 | 26.4% ⚠️ | ### 关键发现 1. **越南发饰市场整体下行** — 所有产品周环比均为负增长（-32%至-39%） 2. **价格带错位** — 越南发饰主流价位在VND 9,000-49,000（≈$0.4-$2.0），低于SOP $1.5最低门槛 3. **毛利率无法达标** — 即使最便宜的1688产品（¥4），毛利率也只有26.4%，远低于SOP 70%红线 4. **无KOL带货** — VN站点带货视频数\\n- Assistant: The message tool requires `text` not `message`. Let me fix that:\\n- Assistant: The selection report has been sent successfully to Feishu. Let me now log this execution to memory.\\n- Assistant: 选品流程执行完成。 ## 执行摘要 ### ✅ 已完成任务 1. **Stage 1 扫描** - 使用 `tiktok_category_name_search` + `tiktok_category_report` + `tiktok_similar_product` 扫描越南发饰品类（Hair Clips 908552 / Headbands 605271） 2. **筛选过滤** - 应用v6.0 SOP标准（价格≥$1.5、星级≥4.2）筛选出候选产品 3. **趋势分析** - 使用 `tiktok_product_tr\\n- Assistant: 无任何KOL带货视频 - ❌ 主流价位$0.4-$2.8（低于$1.5门槛） - ❌ 毛利率40-55%（低于70%红线） **唯一亮点：** Scrunchie发圈周环比+111%，但售价$0.40严重低于最低价红线，建议变体升级至$2+后重新评估。\\n- Assistant: Now let me use mcporter to list available MCP servers and see if Sorftime is configured:\\n- Assistant: The Sorftime MCP server is available with 79 tools. Let me list the available tools to find the specific ones I need for the v6.0 workflow.\\n- Assistant: Let me continue to see more tools available in the sorftime-mcp server, especially looking for the specific tools needed for the v6.0 workflow (tiktok_product_trend, shopee_similar_product, ali1688_similar_product):\\n- Assistant: I found the Sorftime MCP tools. The key tools for the v6.0 workflow are: - `tiktok_similar_product` - for searching TikTok products by keyword - `tiktok_category_name_search` - for category name search - `tiktok_category_report` - for category report (needs nodeId) - `\\n- Assistant: The site parameter wasn't recognized correctly. Let me try using JSON format for the arguments:\\n\\nRecurring themes:\\n- message\\n- tool\\n- requires\\n- parameter\\n- instead\\n- let\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1780945225026,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"7aab95ee\",\n            \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780945225094,\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1779334115229,\n      \"sessionId\": \"68411b9e-c0fa-464a-b416-f59595378be9\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 204000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 4096,\n      \"status\": \"failed\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1779334099698,\n      \"endedAt\": 1779334100119,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 421,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/68411b9e-c0fa-464a-b416-f59595378be9.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"test\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1779334099698,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"ea77510b\",\n            \"recordTimestampMs\": 1779334099915,\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 0,\n            \"totalTokens\": 0,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"error\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1779334100022,\n          \"errorMessage\": \"Anthropic Messages transport requires a positive maxTokens value for minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"03e1044c\",\n            \"recordTimestampMs\": 1779334100027,\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:feishu:group:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"feishu\",\n        \"accountId\": \"kiit\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"feishu:g-ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"la