{"type":"message","id":"36c64dfa","parentId":"15267549","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:27:30.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me look at the key cron sessions that ran and check the actual execution data. I need to check:1. The 5/19 execution - Amazon US Hair Claws, wrote 10 records,毛利率 8-14%\n2. The 6/7 Vietnam execution - 3 records written, all C级\n3. The 6/9 execution - just ran today\n\nLet me check the cron sessions for the older executions. I see:- `agent:tts:cron:5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6` - the old Vietnam cron, with a message about missing tools- `agent:tts:cron:6ee6a981-7b1c-4560-a848-139401e7bfa6` - the new Vietnam v7.0 cron that's still runningLet me look at the 6/7 execution session to understand what happened. Let me check the old cron session transcript.","thinkingSignature":"587849b9e37ffa8202e9246d23c54c733773755ca51eae21b093466e5d8ace9a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5df326a9c21c41cba1c64197","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-06-07.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5459adc8b95f407385234ea0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查旧cron session (5c75bbb4)的历史 -找6/4-6/7的执行记录\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/f542f0c4-257d-42ac-af68-f79d28009844.jsonl 2>/dev/null && wc -l /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/f542f0c4-257d-42ac-af68-f79d28009844.jsonl"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e1747633e54c4c9f811526be","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查5/19之后到6/9之前还有哪些cron执行记录\nfind /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/ -name \"*.jsonl\" -newer /home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-05-19.md 2>/dev/null | sort"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18948,"output":468,"cacheRead":155552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":174968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780990041605,"responseId":"0676f35a51de507ab72e