{"type":"message","id":"667720a4","parentId":"9b25ea02","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a very clear picture. Let me analyze what works and what doesn't:\n\n**Working interfaces (confirmed via curl):**\n1. ✅ `get_time` - works\n2. ✅ `ali1688_similar_product` - works, returns products with Price, Title, Url, Photo, ProductId, StoreName, SalesOf30d, WholesalePriceRange, RepurchaseRate, etc.\n3. ✅ `shopee_product_search` - works for VN/TH, returns products with SalesCount, Price, Ratings, Category, SubCategory, SalesCountOf7D, MonthlySalesGrowth, etc.\n\n\n4. ✅ `shopee_category_search_from_name` - works for VN, returns NodeId + CategoryName (found VN hair accessories: 11036404=Phụ kiện tóc, 11035861=Kẹp tóc, 11035859=Băng đô tóc)\n5. ✅ `tiktok_similar_product` - mcporter failed but curl works\n6. ✅ `tiktok_category_name_search` - mcporter failed but curl might work\n7. ✅ `tiktok_product_trend` - returns product trends\n8. ✅ `tiktok_product_detail` - returns product details\n\nI'm noticing some interfaces fail through mcporter but work directly with curl, particularly the TikTok category and product-related ones, so I should rely on curl for those calls.\n\nLooking at the actual data, `shopee_product_search` gives me SalesCount, Price, Ratings, and MonthlySalesGrowth which are solid sales trend indicators. The `ali1688_similar_product` returns Price, SalesOf30d, and WholesalePriceRange with solid supplier data. The TikTok interfaces give me product trends and details. The Vietnamese node ID 11035861 maps to hair clips, and the Thai shopee_product_search returned results but I need to check if those are actually hair accessories.\n\nLooking at the Thai results, I'm seeing mostly unrelated products like rice cookers, supplements, and oil - not hair accessories. I should try searching with nodeId for Thailand or use keyword searches with hair clip related terms. The `shopee_product_search` interface supports filtering by nodeId and price range, so I need to find the correct Thai category node ID for hair accessories.\n\nThe core issue is that the original SOP assumed `tiktok_product_trend` would give me real-time 24-hour sales data, but I'm actually getting weekly sales counts instead. I need to redesign the SOP to work with what's actually available from these APIs - using `shopee_product_search` to identify trending products by monthly sales growth, then cross-referencing with TikTok data and 1688 pricing. The data I need should come from `shopee_product_search` for platform validation, `tiktok_similar_product` for TikTok performance, `tiktok_product_trend` for trend direction, `tiktok_product_detail` for product info, `ali1688_similar_product` for cost analysis, and `shopee_product_trend` for historical patterns. I should also figure out the category tree for Shopee to properly filter by category.\n","thinkingSignature":"bd72e96cea66e47d6cc41d291f870e84bbc655e05f169ddcfd82ee092e503f43"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n现在我完全摸清了。让我测一下泰国发饰类目ID，然后重写SOP：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1accdbb9e1f14a65960dfe7f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 泰国发饰类目搜索\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://mcp.sorftime.com/\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer rhblyi…qt09\" \\\n  -H \"accept: application/json, text/event-stream\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_category_search_from_name\",\"arguments\":{\"name\":\"hair clip\",\"site\":\"TH\"}},\"id\":6}' 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_63fba6d2b44a41d1881e076c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 越南发饰类目(11035861= Kẹp tóc)趋势 - 找增长最快的发夹\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://mcp.sorftime.com/\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer rhblyi…qt09\" \\\n  -H \"accept: application/json, text/event-stream\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"VN\",\"nodeId\":\"11035861\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":100,\"priceRangeMin\":20000,\"page\":1}},\"id\":7}' 2>&1 | python3 -c \"import sys,json; data=json.load(sys.stdin); products=data.get('result',{}).get('content',[{}])[0]; p=json.loads(products[0]['text']) if isinstance(products[0],dict) else products[0]; prods=p.get('Products',[])[:5]; [print(f\\\"{d['Title'][:40]} | 月销:{d['SalesCount']} | 7天:{d['SalesCountOf7D']} | 增长:{d['MonthlySalesGrowth']}% | 价:{d['Price']} | 星级:{d['Ratings']}\\\") for d in prods]\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"解析失败\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25662,"output":1150,"cacheRead":112226,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139038,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780966900090,"responseId":"067698f5d4d74c1e6ed2c82fc2c910f2"}}
