{"type":"message","id":"eba9b2c3","parentId":"f49ad102","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the cron job for Vietnam and create a new one for Thailand. Let me also update the memory.","thinkingSignature":"6531c95c3d093e2c62d68f790c711f9f1ced098de13f515f4df2ab5c0bca75bd"},{"type":"text","text":"\nSOP v7.0 写完了。现在同步更新 cron 任务，添加泰国：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dtr5hwk34dn5_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"get","jobId":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90594,"output":102,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780989595319,"responseId":"0676f19ca8025d6a4699d06dd344119e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"60af8931","parentId":"eba9b2c3","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dtr5hwk34dn5_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 2136 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"id":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6","name":"TK选品-越南黑马拦截-v6.0","description":"越南市场趋势黑马拦截策略v6.0：每3小时执行阶段1（白天9-21点），S级爆款触发全流程，直接写入飞书多维表格","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779088195684,"updatedAtMs":1780988727423,"agentId":"tts","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行v6.0选品流程（越南市场趋势黑马拦截）：\n\n## 第一步：TikTok扫描\n1. 调用tiktok_product_trend扫描越南发饰品类\n2. 筛选标准（全部满足才通过）：\n   - 24小时销量环比≥100%\n   - 带货视频≥8个\n   - 星级≥4.2\n   - 客单价≥$1.5\n   - 上架时间≤30天\n   - 同款卖家数≤20个\n3. 限取Top 30品\n\n## 第二步：S级爆款判断\n- 12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3 → 标记S级，立即触发完整流程\n\n## 第三步：1688利润核算\n1. 对每个品调用ali1688_similar_product找同款\n2. 毛利率计算：(售价VND - 1688采购价CNY×汇率 - 物流费 - 平台佣金30%) / 售价VND\n   - 物流费 = 售价 × 15%\n   - 平台佣金 = 售价 × 30%\n3. **毛利率必须≥70%才通过**（不是40%，40%会亏损）\n4. 1688采购价必须≤¥5\n\n## 第四步：写入飞书多维表格（20个字段全部填写，禁止留空）\n- app_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n- table_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n\n**写入字段清单（全部必填）：**\n1. 日期 = 当天日期（毫秒时间戳）\n2. 商品名称 = TikTok标题\n3. 站点 = 越南\n4. 选品来源 = [\"Sorftime-TK数据\"]\n5. 采集状态 = 已采集\n6. 三级类目 = 发夹/发圈/抓夹/头饰/发箍\n7. 增长率 = 24小时销量环比（%）\n8. 月销量 = TikTok月销量\n9. 售价（本地货币） = VND售价\n10. 利润率(%) = 计算得出的毛利率（%）\n11. 预估利润 = 售价×利润率\n12. 1688价格(CNY) = 采购价（元）\n13. 1688同款链接 = 1688商品URL\n14. 1688产品主图 = 1688商品主图\n15. 产品连接 = TikTok商品链接\n16. 推荐等级：\n    - S级：毛利率≥70% + 增长率≥100%\n    - A级：毛利率≥70% + 增长率≥50%\n    - B级：毛利率≥60% + 增长率≥30%\n    - C级：毛利率<60% 或增长率<30%\n17. IP风险 = 无/待确认\n18. 行动建议：\n    - S级：立即采购首单50-100件\n    - A级：正常采购首单30-50件\n    - B级：正常采购首选30-50件\n    - C级：观望\n\n## 第五步：发送选品报告到飞书\n- 报告包含：通过商品数量、等级分布、核心爆款信息"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","accountId":"tts"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780999200000,"lastRunAtMs":1780988688650,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":38773,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastDelivered":true}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780989600467}}
{"type":"message","id":"d480c74c","parentId":"60af8931","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the Vietnam cron job to use the new v7.0 SOP, and create a new Thailand cron job. Let me update the Vietnam one first with the new payload that uses Shopee as the primary source instead of TikTok.\n\nThe key changes from v6.0 to v7.0:\n1. Primary data source: Shopee (not TikTok) - use shopee_product_search\n2. Remove the \"带货视频≥8个\" filter (VN data is empty)\n3. Use MonthlySalesGrowth and SalesCountOf7D instead of 24-hour data\n4. Lower the margin threshold to 40% for Vietnam (not 70%)\n\n\n5. Add Thailand job with TH site and nodeId 11046516\n\nI'll need to rewrite the Vietnam job message with the new prompt and create a separate Thailand job, then update MEMORY.md to document the SOP change.","thinkingSignature":"0c28558369d326ea3c5ae987b864604691c5b693f63f0ad91dd80bf4425faa93"},{"type":"text","text":"越南的 cron 也需要更新 payload，用 v7.0 的逻辑。同时新建泰国 cron：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4w3vjzk3rzf5_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6","patch":"{\"name\": \"TK选品-越南黑马-v7.0\", \"description\": \"越南市场选品v7.0：Shopee验证热销→TikTok趋势确认→1688利润终选，毛利率≥40%通过，写入飞书多维表格\", \"payload\": {\"kind\": \"agentTurn\", \"message\": \"执行v7.0选品流程（越南市场）\\n\\n## 第一步：Shopee 产品扫描（主要数据源）\\n用 curl 直调 Sorftime API：\\n```bash\\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\\\" \\\\\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\\\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"jsonrpc\\\":\\\"2.0\\\",\\\"method\\\":\\\"tools/call\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"shopee_product_search\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"site\\\":\\\"VN\\\",\\\"nodeId\\\":\\\"11035861\\\",\\\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\\\":50,\\\"priceRangeMin\\\":20000,\\\"page\\\":1}},\\\"id\\\":1}'\\n```\\n\\n**通过条件（全部满足）：**\\n- 月销量 ≥ 50单\\n- 7天销量 ≥ 月销量×15%（增长苗头）\\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\\n- 上架时间 ≤ 6个月\\n- 好评率 ≥ 90%\\n\\n**重点加分：MonthlySalesGrowth ≥ 30% 或 7天销量 ≥ 500**\\n\\n## 第二步：TikTok 趋势验证\\n用 `tiktok_similar_product` 搜 Shopee 标题关键词，验证 TikTok 上有同款在卖（找到即可，不强制销量门槛）。\\n\\n```bash\\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\\\" \\\\\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\\\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"jsonrpc\\\":\\\"2.0\\\",\\\"method\\\":\\\"tools/call\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"tiktok_similar_product\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"searchName\\\":\\\"产品关键词\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"VN\\\",\\\"page\\\":1}},\\\"id\\\":2}'\\n```\\n\\n**注意：越南TikTok带货视频数据基本为空，不要用视频数量作为筛选条件。**\\n\\n## 第三步：1688 利润终选\\n用 `ali1688_similar_product` 查货源：\\n```bash\\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\\\" \\\\\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\\\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"jsonrpc\\\":\\\"2.0\\\",\\\"method\\\":\\\"tools/call\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"ali1688_similar_product\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"searchName\\\":\\\"产品标题前50字符\\\"}},\\\"id\\\":3}'\\n```\\n\\n**毛利率公式（越南）：**\\n- 毛利率 = 售价×55% - 1688价×汇率/售价\\n- 越南固定成本 ≈ 45%（平台30%+物流10%+仓储5%）\\n- 汇率：1 CNY ≈ 3500 VND\\n\\n**通过条件：**\\n- 1688采购价 ≤ ¥5\\n- 毛利率 ≥ 40%\\n\\n## 第四步：写入飞书多维表格\\n- app_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\\n- table_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\\n- 20个字段全填，不留空\\n\\n## 第五步：发送飞书选品报告\\n- 包含：通过数量、等级分布（S/A/B/C）、核心爆款信息\\n- 站点标注：越南\"}}, \"delivery\": {\"mode\": \"announce\", \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"accountId\": \"tts\"}}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":91789,"output":1163,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147126,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780989600542,"responseId":"0676f1a185f60435586f5701c1181ca4"}}
