{"type":"message","id":"08051fb9","parentId":"c9516c39","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me recreate the Vietnam cron and create a new Thailand cron.","thinkingSignature":"45db228cca8895cafc40b62213c91e6a2211f490ec6366ae28075c22bcebe34e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9scpthy0w0bi_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"TK选品-越南黑马-v7.0","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行v7.0选品流程（越南市场）\n\n## 第一步：Shopee 产品扫描\n用 curl 直调 Sorftime API，搜索越南发夹类目（nodeId=11035861）：\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"VN\",\"nodeId\":\"11035861\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":50,\"priceRangeMin\":20000,\"page\":1}},\"id\":1}'\n```\n\n**通过条件（全部满足）：**\n- 月销量 ≥ 50单\n- 7天销量 ≥ 月销量×15%（增长苗头）\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\n- 上架时间 ≤ 6个月\n- 好评率 ≥ 90%\n\n**重点加分：MonthlySalesGrowth ≥ 30% 或 7天销量 ≥ 500**\n\n## 第二步：TikTok 趋势验证\n用 tiktok_similar_product 搜 Shopee 标题关键词，验证 TikTok 上有同款。\n注意：越南TikTok带货视频数据基本为空，不用视频数量筛选。\n\n## 第三步：1688 利润终选\n用 ali1688_similar_product 查货源：\n\n毛利率公式（越南）：毛利率 = 售价×55% - 1688价×汇率/售价\n越南固定成本 ≈ 45%（平台30%+物流10%+仓储5%），汇率1CNY≈3500VND\n\n**通过条件：1688采购价 ≤ ¥5 且 毛利率 ≥ 40%**\n\n## 第四步：写入飞书多维表格\napp_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\ntable_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n20个字段全填，不留空\n站点标注：越南\n\n## 第五步：发送飞书选品报告\n包含：通过数量、等级分布（S/A/B/C）、核心爆款信息","timeoutSeconds":600},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","accountId":"tts"},"enabled":true}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94339,"output":680,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149193,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780989635326,"responseId":"0676f1c3cdccf050a845ef68a1ed46e7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d16af67f","parentId":"08051fb9","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9scpthy0w0bi_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 1711 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"id":"6ee6a981-7b1c-4560-a848-139401e7bfa6","agentId":"tts","name":"TK选品-越南黑马-v7.0","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780989651228,"updatedAtMs":1780989651228,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行v7.0选品流程（越南市场）\n\n## 第一步：Shopee 产品扫描\n用 curl 直调 Sorftime API，搜索越南发夹类目（nodeId=11035861）：\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"VN\",\"nodeId\":\"11035861\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":50,\"priceRangeMin\":20000,\"page\":1}},\"id\":1}'\n```\n\n**通过条件（全部满足）：**\n- 月销量 ≥ 50单\n- 7天销量 ≥ 月销量×15%（增长苗头）\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\n- 上架时间 ≤ 6个月\n- 好评率 ≥ 90%\n\n**重点加分：MonthlySalesGrowth ≥ 30% 或 7天销量 ≥ 500**\n\n## 第二步：TikTok 趋势验证\n用 tiktok_similar_product 搜 Shopee 标题关键词，验证 TikTok 上有同款。\n注意：越南TikTok带货视频数据基本为空，不用视频数量筛选。\n\n## 第三步：1688 利润终选\n用 ali1688_similar_product 查货源：\n\n毛利率公式（越南）：毛利率 = 售价×55% - 1688价×汇率/售价\n越南固定成本 ≈ 45%（平台30%+物流10%+仓储5%），汇率1CNY≈3500VND\n\n**通过条件：1688采购价 ≤ ¥5 且 毛利率 ≥ 40%**\n\n## 第四步：写入飞书多维表格\napp_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\ntable_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n20个字段全填，不留空\n站点标注：越南\n\n## 第五步：发送飞书选品报告\n包含：通过数量、等级分布（S/A/B/C）、核心爆款信息","timeoutSeconds":600},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","accountId":"tts"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780999200000}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780989651303}}
{"type":"message","id":"c49981d9","parentId":"d16af67f","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me create the Thailand cron job.","thinkingSignature":"9fb053cbe56368e83b872fe0f28619d7434028107ecf2b1cd6571b8177de6ff9"},{"type":"text","text":"越南新建成功。现在创建泰国 cron：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mhcfpbrfvwlr_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"TK选品-泰国黑马-v7.0","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行v7.0选品流程（泰国市场）\n\n## 第一步：Shopee 产品扫描\n用 curl 直调 Sorftime API，搜索泰国发饰品类（nodeId=11046516）：\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"TH\",\"nodeId\":\"11046516\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":50,\"priceRangeMin\":50,\"page\":1}},\"id\":1}'\n```\n\n**通过条件（全部满足）：**\n- 月销量 ≥ 50单\n- 7天销量 ≥ 月销量×15%\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\n- 上架时间 ≤ 6个月\n- 好评率 ≥ 90%\n\n**重点加分：MonthlySalesGrowth ≥ 30% 或 7天销量 ≥ 500**\n\n## 第二步：TikTok 趋势验证\n用 tiktok_similar_product 搜 Shopee 标题关键词，验证 TikTok 上有同款在卖。\n\n## 第三步：1688 利润终选\n用 ali1688_similar_product 查货源：\n\n毛利率公式（泰国）：毛利率 = 售价×52% - 1688价×汇率/售价\n泰国固定成本 ≈ 48%（平台26%+物流12%+仓储5%+退货5%），汇率1CNY≈5 THB\n\n**通过条件：1688采购价 ≤ ¥5 且 毛利率 ≥ 50%**\n（泰国市场竞争更激烈，建议毛利率门槛略高于越南）\n\n## 第四步：写入飞书多维表格\napp_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\ntable_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n20个字段全填，不留空\n站点标注：泰国\n\n## 第五步：发送飞书选品报告\n包含：通过数量、等级分布（S/A/B/C）、核心爆款信息","timeoutSeconds":600},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","accountId":"tts"},"enabled":true}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95775,"output":677,"cacheRead"