{"type":"message","id":"402296a8","parentId":"9db659b4","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both Vietnam and Thailand cron jobs are created. Now let me update the MEMORY.md and daily log.","thinkingSignature":"44872ea5703a6a4ddb2bd1dfebcdd189b66560bd90880f403ea5a9b4967ae64b"},{"type":"text","text":"两个 cron 都建好了。现在更新 MEMORY 和今日日志：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_azvq771l3vr7_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/MEMORY.md","edits":"[{\"oldText\": \"### Cron 任务\\n- TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0：每天 9、12、15、18、21点执行\\n- 30000次额度已购入（2026-06-03）\\n\\n- 选品写入流程已记录（2026-05-20）\\n- SOP v5.2 更新了入场时间窗口过滤器（2026-05-20）\\n- SOP 已同步至飞书文档（2026-05-20）\\n- **BUG修复**：MCP key 写入 shell 变量时截断，导致除 get_time/category_name_search/similar_product_feature 外所有 API 返回 Authentication required。解决：从 /tmp/sorftime_key.txt 读取 key（2026-05-24）\\n- **BUG修复**：飞书 bitable batch_create，app_token 截断版 NOTEXIST，MultiSelect 字段需用数组格式（2026-05-24）\", \"newText\": \"### Cron 任务（v7.0）\\n- TK选品-越南黑马-v7.0：每天 9、12、15、18、21点（cron id: 6ee6a981）\\n- TK选品-泰国黑马-v7.0：每天 9、12、15、18、21点（cron id: dde46f87）\\n\\n### SOP 版本\\n- v6.0 → **v7.0**（2026-06-09）：彻底重写\\n- **核心变更**：数据源从 TikTok 改为 Shopee（TikTok 无批量扫描接口）；越南毛利率门槛从 70% 降至 40%；删除\\\"带货视频≥8\\\"筛选条件（VN数据为空）；新增泰国任务\\n- SOP 文档：/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v7.0.md\\n\\n### 已知限制\\n- API 连续调用过快会报 Authentication required，等待3秒重试即可\\n- 建议用 curl 直调 API，不依赖 mcporter call\\n- curl 格式：`curl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '...'`\"}]"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97202,"output":589,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151965,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780989664538,"responseId":"0676f1e1bb7dc