{"type":"message","id":"19bb0d00","parentId":"59122f50","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:29:21.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also update the daily log.","thinkingSignature":"ec5e8a0209705d07ecc4af8c1296a65eefbfa268ddb77a1d61f4efc70867230b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ce0514so1edq_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-06-09.md","content":"# 2026-06-09每日日志\n\n## 今日完成\n\n### SOP v7.0 重写\n- 彻底解决 v6.0 的致命问题：TikTok 没有批量扫描接口\n- 新核心：Shopee 验证热销（shopee_product_search，可多维筛选）→ TikTok 验证趋势（tiktok_similar_product）→ 1688 利润终选\n- 越南毛利率门槛从 70% 降至 40%（实测越南发饰售价低，45%固定成本导致70%毛利不可能）\n- 删除\"带货视频≥8\"条件（越南数据为空）\n- 新增泰国独立 cron（nodeId=11046516）\n- 文档：/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v7.0.md\n\n### Cron 任务重建\n- 删除旧的越南 v6.0 cron（id: 5c75bbb4）\n- 新建越南 v7.0 cron（id: 6ee6a981）— 每天9/12/15/18/21点\n- 新建泰国 v7.0 cron（id: dde46f87）— 每天9/12/15/18/21点\n\n### API 验证结果\n- shopee_product_search：✅ VN/TH 站点可用，支持 nodeId/价格/月销量/评分过滤\n- shopee_category_search_from_name：✅ 可查类目ID\n- ali1688_similar_product：✅ 返回货源+价格+链接\n- tiktok_similar_product：✅ 有效\n- mcporter call：❌ 连续调用报 Auth，需用 curl 直调\n\n## 待验证\n- 越南发夹 nodeId=11035861 搜索（昨天报错，需再测）\n- 泰国发饰 nodeId=11046516 搜索（已测，有数据）\n\n## 技术备忘\n- curl 调API：Bearer token 从 /tmp/sorftime_key.txt 读取\n- API URL：https://mcp.sorftime.com/\n- 注意：curl 里 key 要用 $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)，不能硬编码带…的字符\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":101649,"output":513,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156336,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780989712718,"responseId":"0676f211752e987a8d78a4908e723c32"}}
