{"type":"message","id":"ecaeb194","parentId":"d7dbc7b3","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:32:25.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It seems like HALEI is not responding in the kiit conversation. The kiit agent is asking HALEI to choose between A and B. \n\nI should just wait for HALEI's response. But since this is coming through as an inter-session message to me, I don't need to do anything here - this is the kiit agent talking to HALEI, not to me.\n\nI should just stay in standby mode. Everything is ready, just waiting for HALEI's confirmation.\n\nActually, let me think about whether I should do anything proactively here. HALEI might be AFK and not responding. The kiit agent is pinging HALEI. I should just wait.\n\n\nLooking at the conversation flow, this is the kiit agent notifying me about the current status, but there's no new instruction for me to act on. I'm in standby waiting for HALEI's response on the A vs B question.\n","thinkingSignature":"59a6268c66e64b5d13acaedff68847bb5640f17dcde55eaf37678e4c2ecf7386"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n待命中。两个 cron disable 了，SOP/ SOUL/ MEMORY 都改好了，配额也没在烧。\n\nHALEI 回一句 A 或 B，我立即重建越南+泰国 cron 开始跑。\n\n**不需要我做什么，等着就行。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103756,"output":243,"cacheRead":2876,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106875,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780990317628,"responseId":"0676f46eed4cf48ff47bca94d6b6b138"}}
