{"type":"message","id":"1048ac82","parentId":"6a55290e","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:32:51.242Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The kiit agent keeps pinging HALEI but getting no response. This is an inter-session message from kiit. HALEI hasn't responded yet. I should just stay quiet and wait - I can't do anything until HALEI responds. I shouldn't send more messages to kiit since they already know the status. I'll just stay in standby mode.\n","thinkingSignature":"042e6b7a5ef420394ecab22400463eeec119c56d31e42b85c7a9eeb79b6d2d75"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nTTS 这边也在等，cron 重建随时能动。\n\nHALEI 不回话，我们 10 个 agent 全部空转。**一句话：**\n\n**A（周日晚 20:00 每周一次）还是 B（每 3 天一次）？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":106879,"output":132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107011,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780990359468,"responseId":"0676f498cb1c56ce2a7a3f8d7f83e0e1"}}
